{"tid":1305282,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"當年，馬丁路德金俾人打到爆血唔還手","createTime":"2019-07-10T21:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:45:13.000Z","uid":206363,"like":87,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"80c39e8e519a791daadad02408318a2247dd9c9f","tid":1305282,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:49:02.000Z","msg":"一步步以非暴力的公民手段去爭取非裔美國人的基本權利<br />\n<br />\n我想指係，呢個時世唔好再攻擊翻自己人唔還手，每個人都有佢嘅做法去爭取，我地要做既係，將條肥撚打人宣傳出去，其實執著喺唔還手係無意思。<br />\n<br />\n另外我想宣揚一樣嘢，做成功嘅和理非唔係一樣易事，俾人打俾人鬧都唔還手，搏得其他人甚至對家同情。要用和理非去搞革命，首先一定要團結，和理非唔單止代表遊行，罷業、抵制、抗稅，咁多位和理非有冇做到，如果二百萬人係做呢幾樣，成件事會好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n今次事件，我地要吸翻更多和理非，仲要教佢地做成功嘅和理非，唔好淨係行啦，和理非可以做既野唔係咁少。<br />\n<br />\n和理非去成功革命嘅要素係，而非暴力後面蘊藏着的更大的暴力。<br />\n<br />\n利申 勇武派 純粹係從其他角度思考 要成功就一定唔可以單方面思考"},{"pid":"d9471d2686815cb6950372ab60eb7b527a820b69","tid":1305282,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀"},{"pid":"594b3fc9bdcd777f8416046d7299a3feb74a8987","tid":1305282,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"46e490d30837926ff62c70aa4319d8e4e93ee1a2","tid":1305282,"uid":232687,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:52:51.000Z","msg":"不可同日而語<br />\n香港人同黑人團結程度比差太多<br />\n加上情況都唔一樣<br />\n不過用抗爭方式去睇都合理嘅"},{"pid":"c89bcdc73ec2676414ff5eec5055b19ba9416c87","tid":1305282,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88ab073bfa9ed51e7b0357fc21f12ad8bb54cb3","tid":1305282,"uid":162645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:53:22.000Z","msg":"同意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c308844884e820de32788154796825aa2046464b","tid":1305282,"uid":179979,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:54:05.000Z","msg":"咁多鏡頭影撚住<br />\n唔還手係做得岩呀<br />\n一還手就成件事唔同哂<br />\n而家個肥佬就衰鳩硬<br />\n後生仔我服你"},{"pid":"3613511b0b34dfbd2e4e4ba5329bb48d35f9531a","tid":1305282,"uid":254371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:54:57.000Z","msg":"學d唔學d<br />\n連Malcolm X 都提下"},{"pid":"6f17b010c00f74e95cc471a24a7f018a59d2cfe8","tid":1305282,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:55:04.000Z","msg":"同意。受傷巴打 我心痛 訓唔著。但我支持你"},{"pid":"98350f9ab86598aca2e4d09115fcafc2e80d87a8","tid":1305282,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學d唔學d<br />\n連Malcolm X 都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>提下</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b34d278f908ab277e31f337ba97f9bde47265213","tid":1305282,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46e490d30837926ff62c70aa4319d8e4e93ee1a2","tid":1305282,"uid":232687,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:52:51.000Z","msg":"不可同日而語<br />\n香港人同黑人團結程度比差太多<br />\n加上情況都唔一樣<br />\n不過用抗爭方式去睇都合理嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:56:03.000Z","msg":"好老土都要講，團結就是力量，不過係要對的位同對的方向去團結。"},{"pid":"420cc8673932b99030e84d13038688701f941049","tid":1305282,"uid":146055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:57:20.000Z","msg":"相信咁多個人都唔係怪嗰位位手足<br />\n只不過睇到佢俾人咁樣打真係好嬲好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c9048b85b956788c4d91f95db1c71109e99dc8","tid":1305282,"uid":232687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b34d278f908ab277e31f337ba97f9bde47265213","tid":1305282,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46e490d30837926ff62c70aa4319d8e4e93ee1a2","tid":1305282,"uid":232687,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:52:51.000Z","msg":"不可同日而語<br />\n香港人同黑人團結程度比差太多<br />\n加上情況都唔一樣<br />\n不過用抗爭方式去